Articles.Content:
Hello again today i present to you my biggest moment of happiness

Look at the mountains and.... YEAH THE TEMPLE!.

I wasn't looking for it, i was running a battery powered mapping unit from launch to end, and after depleting 8250 Ec (And other 3200 on 4 capacitors) It was ready to return whit enough data, during descent i found this, Im so happy about this
Hey, didn't know they were above the terrain! It's been a while since I last saw them.
